      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The regular monthly meeting Of\nthe 10000 club will be held tonight\nin the Moorish room of the Spo-\nkane hotel. An address will be\nmade by Horace l.. Mcintyre, as\nsistant city engineer, on Irrigation\nand Its Influence on Spokane\" and\nw. H. Ludden will speak on\nphase of Municipal Life From a\nLawyers Point of View\"\n\n\nAll are invited to attend the meet\ning whether they are boosters or\nnot."
